metadata.dc:description: We present a one-year study describing the ENT pathology seen in a rural ENT clinic. The study included 1,516 patients whose characteristics are described (age, sex, diagnosis, and others).
metadata.dc:title: Asistencia primaria en otorrinolaringología. Estudio descriptivo.
[Primary health care in otorhinolaryngology. Descriptive study].
